    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "For sale is a dependable vehicle in fair condition, ideal for a daily commuter who prioritizes mechanical reliability over aesthetic perfection. The engine and transmission are solid and perform well, but the car does show its age with several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the upholstery. It has been regularly maintained, though it will eventually need minor suspension work and new tires in the coming months. This is a straightforward, honest car that gets the job done without any hidden surprises.",
