    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained E46 M3, powered by the legendary S54 atmospheric inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. This example features the desirable 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring a visceral connection to the tarmac. The chassis maintains excellent torsional rigidity with a documented subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and a complete cooling system overhaul. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical vitals remain sharp, offering the high-revving throttle response and balanced weight distribution this chassis is renowned for.",
      "price": 34800.0,
