    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of pride of ownership, blending reliable performance with a well-preserved aesthetic. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a keen eye might notice a few minor stone chips and light surface marks typical of a well-loved daily driver. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the premium leather seats remain supple with only slight softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and every button, dial, and digital display functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health, having benefited from a consistent schedule of synthetic oil changes and a recent full brake service. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the engine provides smooth, responsive power. It sits on a set of high-quality tires with plenty of tread remaining, ensuring a quiet and confident ride. Complete with a full service history and two sets of keys, this car is ready for its next chapter without needing immediate attention.",
